{"tid":927677,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"圓號法國號法蘭西號大喇叭交流區","createTime":"2018-12-04T10:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T05:00:52.000Z","uid":141800,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8b5ff1924a22445ecf2cdbf32e27883b1f96431","tid":927677,"uid":141800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T10:18:15.000Z","msg":"有冇人有玩過下圓號呢種樂器？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gebr-alexander.de/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/200-Doppelhorn-frei-VS-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgebr-alexander.de%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F200-Doppelhorn-frei-VS-2.jpg&h=ed012eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟我多年前有認真玩過下 細過嗰陣覺得佢幾得意閃令令好靚就走鬼左去拜師學藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  嗰時一學就差唔多有十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由細細粒人仔開始背着個砘幾重嘅大龜殼 去到尖沙咀上堂 到今時今日算係知道下圓號有咩特色 都付出左唔少嘅心血同努力<br />\n<br />\n龜殼示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0166/4396/products/iP316SB-SCall-1.jpg?v=1449081963\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F0166%2F4396%2Fproducts%2FiP316SB-SCall-1.jpg%3Fv%3D1449081963&h=99261e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRykr0yjbutTNWSbEOG-MyMJs51RQnPKYUD5SRAd85wBMpbiL7i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRykr0yjbutTNWSbEOG-MyMJs51RQnPKYUD5SRAd85wBMpbiL7i&h=bca2ef26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以小弟我今日忽發奇想 想同大家分享一下圓號嘅少少特色同音樂 除左為圓號添加一下知名度之外 亦係為自己嘅音樂知識來一個重温<br />\n<br />\n圓號嘅可恨之處就係睇佢得幾粒制以為好簡單好易學！ 其實佢係世上十大最難掌握嘅樂器之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(According to: <a href=\"https://consordini.com/most-difficult-instruments-to-learn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fconsordini.com%2Fmost-difficult-instruments-to-learn%2F&d=%2BFVF%2B%2B1LFjZFrUFcUGgE7cP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=5ce2d706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://consordini.com/most-difficult-instruments-to-learn/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n學習圓號第一個基本嘅要求就係強大嘅肺活量！ <br />\n眾所週知 吹喇叭越長氣越着數 但係你又知唔知 其實圓號如果要上高音 其實係要以超快嘅速度吹氣 而低音就需要以穩定嘅慢速吹氣 一首稍為有啲旋律嘅歌對肺活量嘅要求係絕對不少！<br />\n<br />\n而第二個要求就係基本樂理知識 <br />\n唔好以為識睇譜就得 圓號其實係in F 㗎！意思即係圓號嘅高音C 就等於鋼琴嘅 F 一樣 假如圓號想演奏其他樂器嘅樂譜或者係樂團表演嗰陣無圓號專用譜嘅話 圓號手係需要自行翻譯自己份樂譜㗎<br />\n<br />\n第三個要求就係基本記憶能力<br />\n現今社會上嘅圓號都普遍係 Double Horn  意思即係除左 in F 之外 仲有 in Bb 嘅調 而佢嘅原理亦都好簡單 就係喺圓號上面加多一列唔同長度嘅管道 令到圓號手可以因應情況使用兩種不同嘅調 記得我老師當年嘅講法就係低音就用 Bb 可以令音色具厚度  而高音用 F 可以令音色清脆且更準確性<br />\n<br />\nDouble Horn 圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://gebr-alexander.de/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/200-Doppelhorn-frei-VS-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgebr-alexander.de%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2F200-Doppelhorn-frei-VS-2.jpg&h=ed012eb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSingle Horn 圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://az58332.vo.msecnd.net/e88dd2e9fff747f090c792316c22131c/Images/Products210543-371x350&ndash;505150206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faz58332.vo.msecnd.net%2Fe88dd2e9fff747f090c792316c22131c%2FImages%2FProducts210543-371x350%E2%80%93505150206.jpg&h=eeb81d59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四個嘅要求就係氣嘅控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要吹準一個音除左係指法上要熟悉之外 仲要控制好你道氣  需知道同一個指法係可以吹到好幾個音符 假如用太少氣 或者太多就會吹錯音 圓號之所以難掌握亦都係因為準確度難控制<br />\n<br />\n以下係一段圓號嘅獨奏<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EQH0C5yB6JI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEQH0C5yB6JI&d=%2BFVF%2B%2B1LFjZFrUFcUGgE7cP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=662d8050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EQH0C5yB6JI</a><br />\n<br />\n只要掌握得好 其實大喇叭都可以好好聽㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我會不定時更新有關圓號嘅二三事 有興趣嘅都可以一齊分享一下音樂㗎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f35291ffe6cf8c199f5379cebfb69d053a7b98","tid":927677,"uid":208293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"我都有學過<br />\n奈何唔夠氣，吹到頂會頭暈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac70a0ceb4129110df795861ca1f3de55019bc4","tid":927677,"uid":141800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27f35291ffe6cf8c199f5379cebfb69d053a7b98","tid":927677,"uid":208293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"我都有學過<br />\n奈何唔夠氣，吹到頂會頭暈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"所以話 圓號真係唔啱小朋友或者氣量唔夠嘅人學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟我當年都係堂堂都好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809e4a0448bcc2f90e1816b8e47cb6dc41a343cf","tid":927677,"uid":166409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"中學考完8級就冇玩 依家擺係度封緊塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43045a60aefe23467916ce23b77b5478363688c0","tid":927677,"uid":141800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"809e4a0448bcc2f90e1816b8e47cb6dc41a343cf","tid":927677,"uid":166409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"中學考完8級就冇玩 依家擺係度封緊塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"我都係 都唔知幾奈無清潔過<br />\n當年清潔得好講究！ 有分管油 火箭油同專登去日本買嘅用黎滴入去啲制內部嘅油<br />\n而家一打翻開相信啲制已經硬到拑唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ffe9ec6e4e3ff2c95695c77b0c30674c6918e4","tid":927677,"uid":141800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:07:47.000Z","msg"